data.description: East Passyunk Avenue Lifestyle:  Immerse yourself in the unique charm and character of East Passyunk Avenue, known for its eclectic mix of boutiques, restaurants, and cultural events. This starter home offers not only a convenient and practical living space but also the potential to grow and adapt to your changing needs. Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own and experience the best of city living..  The heart of this home is the large kitchen, providing ample space for culinary enthusiasts and gatherings. Adjacent dining room allows for comfortable family meals and entertaining . Proximity to East Passyunk Avenue ensures you're just steps away from trendy shops, delightful eateries, and a lively community atmosphere. Welcome to your perfect starter home!
